>akonadiconsole</varname
>. Do not worry, this high memory usage is <emphasis
>only</emphasis
> for initial import.
</para>
<para
>Initiate a check mail for POP3 resources.
</para>
</listitem>
</orderedlist>
<para
>Hopefully after these steps, you will have a much nicer &kmail; experience.
</para>
</sect1
